item.title: Introduction
item.description: The first week of CS61A is pretty simple - get used to your coding environment and a few of the basics of Python. Lab 0 # While this is optional, it’s probably best to do it just to get used to the very basics of Python as well as ok.py, the autograder used in CS61A.
